tools.description:
Scene management — open/save/create scenes, get hierarchy, check readiness.
Actions: get_info, hierarchy, list, open, save, create, is_ready.
Example: {action:"hierarchy"} or {action:"create", name:"GamePlay"}

Prefab management — create/list/delete/instantiate prefabs, unlink instances.
Actions: create, list, instantiate, unlink, delete.
Example: {action:"create", node:"Canvas/Enemy", prefabPath:"db://assets/prefabs/Enemy.prefab"}

Editor utilities — project info, console logs, run/stop preview.
Actions: project_info, project_settings, run, stop, console_logs, console_clear, mcp_log_read, mcp_log_clear, editor_info.
Example: {action:"project_info"} or {action:"run"}

Viewport control — gizmo tools, camera focus.
Actions: gizmo_tool, gizmo_tool_query, camera_focus, camera_reset, status.
Example: {action:"camera_focus", nodes:["Player"]} or {action:"gizmo_tool", tool:"position"}

One-call UI creation (2.x) — create Button/Label/Image/Toggle/Slider/ProgressBar/EditBox/ScrollView/PageView/RichText/Layout/Mask/Graphics/Spine, Widget, batch.
Actions: create_button, create_label, create_image, create_toggle, create_slider, create_progressbar, create_editbox, create_scrollview, create_pageview, create_richtext, create_layout, create_mask, create_graphics, create_spine, setup_widget, batch, batch_create_button, batch_create_label, batch_create_image, batch_create_toggle, batch_create_slider, batch_create_progressbar, batch_create_editbox.
Example: {action:"create_button", parent:"Canvas", name:"StartBtn", text:"Start", fontSize:28}
Batch: {action:"batch_create_button", parent:"Canvas/Panel", items:[{name:"Btn1",text:"OK"},{name:"Btn2",text:"Cancel"}]}

Knowledge base — component properties, UI design rules, layout patterns, widget strategy.
Topics: component_properties, ui_design_rules, layout_patterns, widget_strategy, node_structure, best_practices, tool_guide.
Example: {action:"component_properties", query:"cc.Sprite"} or {action:"tool_guide", query:"node"}

Validation tools (2.x) — layout overlap/offscreen, reference consistency, hierarchy depth.
Actions: layout (size/font/touch issues), references (missing scripts), hierarchy (depth/naming).
Example: {action:"layout"} or {action:"references"}

UI templates (2.x) — apply pre-built structures (dialog, scroll_list, nav_bar, settings_page).
Actions: list, apply.
Example: {action:"list"} or {action:"apply", template:"dialog", parent:"Canvas"}

Animation editing (2.x) — clips, presets, batch file writing.
Primary method: batch_file (writes .anim directly, no edit mode needed).
Use preset for common animations (fade, bounce, shake, slide, etc.).
Actions: query_clips, query_clip_info, query_state, play, pause, resume, stop, change_sample, change_speed, change_wrap_mode, create_clip, batch_file, preset_list, preset.
Example: {action:"preset", clipUuid:"...", preset:"sprite_fade_in"}
Example: {action:"batch_file", clipUuid:"...", data:{tracks:[{propKey:"opacity",keyframes:[{frame:0,value:0},{frame:30,value:255}]}]}}

Label & Text (2.x) — manage cc.Label, cc.RichText, cc.EditBox.
Actions: info, list, set_text, set_font, set_style, set_outline, set_shadow, batch_set_font, batch_set_style.
Example: {action:"set_text", node:"Title", text:"Hello"}
{action:"set_style", node:"Title", fontSize:32, isBold:true, color:{r:255,g:0,b:0}}
{action:"batch_set_font", useSystemFont:true, fontFamily:"Arial"}

[DEV-ONLY] Component exploration (2.x).
Actions: explore_component (create temp node + add component + dump properties), list_component_properties (dump properties of existing component on a node).
Example: {action:"explore_component", componentType:"cc.Button"}
{action:"list_component_properties", node:"Canvas/Btn", componentType:"cc.Button"}
